document_data.Notable Treants:
*[[Sequaxion]], a treant who lived in the garden of the [[For-Rest Inn]] in [[Ravens Bluff]] and acted as its gardener.{{Cite polyhedron/49/The Living City: The For-Rest Inn|29}}
*[[Seven seedlings of the verdant sages]], a group of immature offspring of the most ancient and wisest treants of [[the North]] known of in the mid–14{{th}} century [[DR]].
*[[Turlang]], a treant who guarded the northwestern region of the [[High Forest]], a grove known as [[Turlang's Wood]].
